ABN AMRO acquires stake in S - African broker . ABN AMRO Bank said on Thursday its unit ABN AMRO Hoare Govett had acquired a 40 percent stake in the South African broker Huysamer Stals together with Kasogo Financial Services . The biggest shareholders in KSF are NM Rothschilds & Sons and Kasigo Trust Investment Company in South Africa . ABN AMRO also said it had acquired a minority stake in KFS . 
